However, in view of this approach by mobile providers, the Czech regulatory authorities are surprised by the absolute disinterest.
This is not just the attitude of the ČTÜ, which unfortunately, in Czech, in contrast to the UK and other highly developed countries, does not have the competence to intervene in economic competition.
